name: xTherm
body:
### Welcome to xTherm
xTherm is an open source CPU temperature monitor for mac OSX. 

### Supported Systems
OS X 10.11 (El Capitan)

### Contributing
We love contributions, so head over to our [github](https://github.com/arc3x/xTherm) and file an issue, request an enhancement, or make a pull request.

### Authors and Contributors
Matthew Slocum (@arc3x)
Sami Sahli (@ssahli)
